{
  "id": "RAW_3ffbc857",
  "title": "DeepSeek 王炸：10 倍压缩率，97%解码精度！上下文光学压缩登场",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3MTkxMjYzOA==&mid=2247508716&idx=1&sn=6f4662f58c6c9eddbb570cb04b240275",
  "date": "2025-10-20 08:16:00",
  "author": "AI寒武纪",
  "siteName": "AI寒武纪",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;white-space: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100025057\" data-ratio=\"0.2814814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4fe6ffa9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0UcofQ9Eq1NVGR6RibdkKuUS5ghrQfhAM1sbz7Lf8Yd0an6R9TfXXnprGibLtTUBicCOiaYiblnicOmljSg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"AI寒武纪\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/ICgnAptln0Xg6w3lVHUFXrtY5Tia7rfUDkTmCwe5Gz5RRAtVR2CX6UgcZiaFWnxksH1fkSSmjxichSCic8CTGqcElA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"一起见证人工智能的寒武纪大爆发，传播一切有关AI的技术\" data-id=\"Mzg3MTkxMjYzOA==\"></mp-common-profile></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;margin: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px 8px 1.5em;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">来自DeepSeek的最新研究：</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek-OCR</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，一种探索通过光学2D映射来压缩长上下文的新方法</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">LLM处理长文本的计算成本，又有了新的破解思路。把长长的上下文，直接渲染成一张图片，再喂给模型，这样做的好处是，原本数千上万个文本token，现在可能只需要几百个视觉token就能表示，实现了信息的高效压缩</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">实验结果相当惊人：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在压缩率小于</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">10倍</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">时（即文本token数是视觉token数的10倍以内），模型OCR解码准确率高达</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">97%</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">即使在</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">20倍</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的超高压缩率下，准确率依然能保持在</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">60%</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;左右</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在主流的文档解析基准测试 OmniDocBench 上，DeepSeek-OCR 用更少的视觉token，实现了超越SOTA模型的性能</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">更重要的是，这项技术不仅是科研探索，还具备极高的实用价值。在生产环境中，单台A100-40G GPU每天就能处理超过</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">20万页</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的文档，为大模型训练提供海量数据</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前，相关的代码和模型权重均已开源</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-OCR/\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-OCR/</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-OCR\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-OCR</a></span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">什么是“上下文光学压缩”？</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">LLM在处理长文本时，面临的核心挑战是其固有的二次方计算复杂度。随着序列长度的增加，计算资源和时间会急剧增长。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek研究人员提出了一个反直觉却又合乎逻辑的想法：利用视觉模态作为文本信息的压缩媒介</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">相比于一长串的数字文本token，一张包含同样内容的文档图像，可以用远少于前者的视觉token来表示。这就好比将一本书的内容拍成一张照片，这张照片本身就包含了所有的文字和排版信息</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种“文本→图像→视觉token”的转换过程，就是所谓的</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">上下文光学压缩</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（Contexts Optical Compression）</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了验证这一想法，团队构建了DeepSeek-OCR模型。从图（a）的压缩实验中可以看出，视觉token数量和OCR解码精度之间的权衡关系：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100025049\" data-ratio=\"0.8148148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cf0e11b5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0UcofQ9Eq1NVGR6RibdkKuUSo8SKQOwdry2Sl3OBF6wVic0EVLsGqXfHEicNibezf2FHZDHhwKYJrNDOQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">64个视觉token</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（左侧柱状图）：当文本token数在600-700之间（压缩率约10.5倍）时，精度为96.5%。随着文本量增加到1200-1300（压缩率接近20倍），精度下降到59.1%</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">100个视觉token</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（右侧柱状图）：在600-700文本token（压缩率6.7倍）时，精度高达98.5%。即使文本量增加，压缩率达到12.6倍时，精度仍有87.1%</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这意味着，在10倍压缩的范围内，模型几乎可以“无损”地从图像中解码出原文</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek-OCR是如何实现的？</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek-OCR的架构由两部分组成：一个核心的编码器</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepEncoder</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，和一个解码器</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek3B-MoE-A570M</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100025050\" data-ratio=\"0.3351851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e3762bb7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0UcofQ9Eq1NVGR6RibdkKuUSSDUZYWr8GITCBoOwyYksu0tMUEVa7qtqfadn0AVtvauO25lkK8xUPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">解码器采用了高效的MoE（Mixture-of-Experts）架构，而整个系统的创新关键在于DeepEncoder</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了在处理高分辨率图像时，依然能保持较低的计算激活和可控的视觉token数量，DeepEncoder的架构设计非常巧妙，它串联了三个关键组件：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">SAM-base (ViTDet)</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：利用窗口注意力（window attention）机制处理局部感知，将输入图像（如1024x1024）分割成大量patch（如4096个）。由于是窗口注意力且模型规模不大（80M），激活值是可控的</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">16倍卷积压缩器</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：在特征进入全局注意力模块前，通过一个2层卷积网络进行16倍的下采样，将视觉token数量从4096个锐减到256个</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">3.</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">CLIP-large (ViT)</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：利用密集的全局注意力（dense global attention）机制提取视觉知识。由于输入的token数量已经大幅减少，这里的计算开销也变得可以接受</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种“先局部处理，再压缩，后全局理解”的串行设计，使得DeepEncoder能够在处理高清图像的同时，生成数量极少的视觉token，实现了内存和token的双重压缩</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">效果炸裂，token用得还少</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在权威的文档理解基准&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">OmniDocBench</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;上，DeepSeek-OCR展现了其卓越的实用性能。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100025051\" data-ratio=\"0.8148148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c12dde2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0UcofQ9Eq1NVGR6RibdkKuUSPva6pxFdpsBd1PxrH6AX9AjgwdjlQibuAF8kcwpObJ94uBFu9pjUyNA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">从上图的性能对比中可以看出，DeepSeek-OCR（红色圆点）在“平均每张图的视觉token数”（横轴）上处于最右侧区域，意味着它使用的token数量最少。而在“整体性能（编辑距离）”（纵轴，越低越好）上，它却达到了SOTA水平</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">具体来看：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">仅用100个视觉token（Small模式），就超越了使用256个token的 GOT-OCR2.0</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用不到800个视觉token（Gundam模式），性能就超过了需要 6000+ token的 MinerU2.0</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这充分证明，DeepSeek-OCR在实际应用中非常强大，并且由于其极高的token压缩率，为未来的研究留下了更高的想象空间</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">不止于OCR的“深度解析”</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了常规的OCR能力，DeepSeek-OCR还具备对文档内图像进行深度解析的能力</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">无论是金融研报里的</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">图表</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100025052\" data-ratio=\"1.2153558052434457\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1068\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=20b25ca8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0UcofQ9Eq1NVGR6RibdkKuUSlz5QSsFiaQuD0ItxKhrAF5oY7uMNoYa4emjldfY1jjUtVwFW8IAKmtw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">还是化学文献里的</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">分子式</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100025053\" data-ratio=\"1.2348484848484849\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1056\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ea0cc371&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0UcofQ9Eq1NVGR6RibdkKuUSnszGmoq70jpQ9HH9KABJibsW6fUVCngJrb5vJ8EEXnCFAzZsm0wdOUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">甚至是数学题中的</span><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">几何图形</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，它都能进行结构化的解析和转换</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100025054\" data-ratio=\"1.135755258126195\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1046\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=62d0ab01&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0UcofQ9Eq1NVGR6RibdkKuUSmgfYd5XXtFAoU6uuS1zXSmXxP9eXvoic0JjwGWFoFbnqiccJD1EGEpBA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，得益于其多语言的训练数据，模型还能处理包括阿拉伯语、僧伽罗语在内的近百种语言的文档</span></p>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0px;border-left:3px solid rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight:bold;padding-left:8px;font-size:16.5px;line-height:1.2;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">未来构想：模拟人类记忆遗忘</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这项研究最引人遐想的部分，是它为实现LLM的记忆遗忘机制提供了一种可能的路径</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">研究人员将上下文光学压缩与人类记忆的衰退过程进行了类比：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100025055\" data-ratio=\"0.3559322033898305\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1062\" type=\"block\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d67fa1a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FICgnAptln0UcofQ9Eq1NVGR6RibdkKuUSkJcabickkFyibSJPtticDib4DWh0RN3ZDJBcUrcXu4arwWETAbkGb0WPLQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">近期记忆</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;(Recent Contexts)：就像近处的物体，清晰可见。可以将其渲染成高分辨率图像，用较多的视觉token来保留高保真信息</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(183, 110, 121);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">远期记忆</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;(Older Contexts)：就像远处的物体，逐渐模糊。可以将其渐进式地缩放成更小、更模糊的图像，用更少的视觉token来表示，从而实现信息的自然遗忘和压缩</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过这种方式，模型可以在处理超长对话或文档时，动态地为不同时期的上下文分配不同数量的计算资源，从而可能构建出一种理论上无限长上下文的架构。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">总而言之，DeepSeek-OCR不仅验证了“上下文光学压缩”这一新颖想法的可行性，还提供了一个性能强大、极具实用价值的开源模型，为解决LLM的长上下文难题开辟了一个全新的、充满希望的方向。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文地址：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"http://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-OCR\" target=\"_blank\">http://github.com/deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-OCR</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 0px;line-height: 0;margin: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "DeepSeek-OCR 通过上下文光学压缩，以高达 10 倍的压缩率和 97%的解码精度，为解决 LLM 长上下文难题提供了创新性视觉模态解决方案。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "DeepSeek-OCR 通过上下文光学压缩，以高达 10 倍的压缩率和 97%的解码精度，为解决 LLM 长上下文难题提供了创新性视觉模态解决方案。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 DeepSeek 团队的最新研究——DeepSeek-OCR，该模型提出了一种名为“上下文光学压缩”的新方法，旨在解决大型语言模型（LLM）处理长文本时面临的二次方计算复杂度问题。其核心思想是将长文本上下文渲染成一张图片，然后将其作为视觉 token 输入给模型，从而实现信息的高效压缩。实验结果显示，在压缩率小于 10 倍时，DeepSeek-OCR 的 OCR 解码准确率高达 97%。在权威的 OmniDocBench 基准测试中，DeepSeek-OCR 以更少的视觉 token 实现了超越 SOTA 模型的性能。文章还深入解析了 DeepSeek-OCR 的架构，特别是 DeepEncoder 通过串联 SAM-base、16 倍卷积压缩器和 CLIP-large，实现了“先局部处理、再压缩、后全局理解”的巧妙设计，从而在处理高分辨率图像的同时，生成数量极少的视觉 token。此外，模型不仅具备强大的 OCR 能力，还能深度解析文档中的图表、分子式和几何图形等图像信息，并支持近百种语言。研究还展望了该技术在模拟人类记忆遗忘机制，构建理论上无限长上下文 LLM 方面的巨大潜力。相关代码和模型权重均已开源。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "DeepSeek-OCR 通过将长文本渲染为图像实现上下文光学压缩，显著降低 LLM 处理长文本的计算成本。",
      "explanation": "传统 LLM 处理长文本面临二次方计算复杂度，而 DeepSeek-OCR 将数千文本 token 压缩为数百视觉 token，在 10 倍压缩率下仍保持 97%解码精度，有效缓解了这一难题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "DeepEncoder 采用独特的“先局部处理，再压缩，后全局理解”架构，高效处理高分辨率图像并生成极少视觉 token。",
      "explanation": "DeepEncoder 串联 SAM-base、16 倍卷积压缩器和 CLIP-large，通过窗口注意力、下采样和全局注意力机制，在保证处理高清图像的同时，实现了内存和 token 的双重高效压缩。"
    },
    {
      "point": "DeepSeek-OCR 不仅具备 SOTA 的 OCR 性能，还能深度解析文档内图像内容，并为 LLM 记忆遗忘机制提供新思路。",
      "explanation": "模型在 OmniDocBench 上表现卓越，能识别图表、分子式、几何图形等，并支持多语言。其对上下文的渐进式压缩与人类记忆遗忘类比，为构建理论上无限长上下文的 LLM 开辟了新方向。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
